This is an unofficial collection of all the music from the Electra Heart era. You can not buy this edition in stores or online. I have compiled it myself. This collection includes the original deluxe version of the album. It also includes a live version of 'Lies' with a new verse, American bonus track 'How to be a Heartbreaker', 3 more tracks released after the album including a collaboration with Charli XCX and the elusive title track. And for the really big fans, a demo version of 'Miss Y'. I've slightly reordered the tracklist and attached a fan made album cover. The whole album is properly tagged for easy sorting.Enjoy =]

Please, please, please SEED!!! And if you love the album/artist, then please buy and support =]
